text: "Precious" is a 1992 song by Scottish singer Annie Lennox and is the second single from her debut studio album Diva. It went to number 23 in the United Kingdom, number 7 in Italy, number 83 in Australia, number 49 in Germany and number 39 in the Netherlands. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:1992 songs Category:Annie Lennox songs
